'''Airspeeders for Bodyguards and Security Specialists''' was a training course that covered [[Airspeeder/Legends|airspeeder]] [[Pilot/Legends|piloting]]. Intended for [[Bodyguard/Legends|bodyguards]] and security officers, it was held on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. [[Joram Kithe]] attended this course at one point.<ref name="Pengalan">{{InsiderCite|65|The Pengalan Tradeoff|reprint=1}}</ref>

